  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the robata-grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together sea salt, black pepper, garlic powder, and ginger powder.",
    "Add the chicken tendon to the bowl and toss to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Brush the robata-grill with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Grill the chicken tendon for 5-7 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together soy sauce and honey.",
    "Brush the soy sauce mixture onto the grilled chicken tendon.",
    "Sprinkle chopped green onions and sesame seeds onto the chicken tendon.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
  ],
